## `search-multiple`

**Usage**:

```console
$ search-multiple [OPTIONS]
```

**Options**:

* `--address TEXT`
* `--name TEXT`
* `--street TEXT`
* `--number TEXT`
* `--code TEXT`
* `--language [EN|LAV]`: [default: Language.EN]
* `--help`: Show this message and exit.

